RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT CCY_RATE_TYPE,CCY_RATE_TYPE_DESC FROM CYTM_RATE_TYPE

SELECT DISTINCT A.RATE_TYPE CCY_RATE_CODE, C.CCY_RATE_TYPE_DESC CCY_RATE_DESC FROM CYTMS_RATES A, CYTMS_RATES_MASTER B, CYTMS_RATE_TYPE C WHERE A.RATE_TYPE = C.CCY_RATE_TYPE AND A.BRANCH_CODE = B.BRANCH_CODE AND A.CCY1 = B.CCY1 AND A.CCY2 = B.CCY2 AND B.AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND A.BRANCH_CODE = GLOBAL.CURRENT_BRANCH
SELECT CCY_CODE FROM CYTMS_CCY_DEFN WHERE RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A' UNION SELECT '*.*' FROM DUAL
SELECT CLUSTER_ID, CLUSTER_DESC FROM OLTMS_CLUSTER_MASTER ORDER BY CLUSTER_ID

SELECT X.COMPONENT, X.COMPONENT_DESCRIPTION FROM LFTMS_PRODUCT_ICCF_TEMP X, LFTB_ICCF_RLAVL Y WHERE X.PRODUCT = ? AND X.RULE = Y.RULE_ID AND Y.RULE_TYPE = 'I' AND NVL(X.CONSIDER_FOR_LIQ, 'Y') = 'Y' AND COMPONENT NOT IN (SELECT CLASS_CODE FROM LFTM_INTEREST_CLASS A WHERE A.ALLOW_REPORTING_ONLY = 'Y' OR A.CREDIT_COMPONENT = 'Y') UNION SELECT 'PRINCIPAL', 'PRINCIPAL' FROM DUAL UNION SELECT X.COMPONENT, X.COMPONENT_DESCRIPTION FROM LFTMS_PRODUCT_ICCF_TEMP X, LFTM_FEE_CLASS Y WHERE X.PRODUCT =? AND X.COMPONENT = Y.CLASS_CODE AND Y.MODULE=?
SELECT PRODUCT_GROUP, PRODUCT_GROUP_DESCRIPTION FROM OLTMS_PRODUCT_GROUP WHERE RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A'
SELECT FORMAT_NAME, FORMAT_DESCRIPTION FROM OLTMS_USERREF_FORMAT_MASTER
SELECT CCY_CODE, CCY_NAME FROM CYTMS_CCY_DEFN WHERE RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A'
SELECT DISTINCT CFTM_FLOATING_RATE_CODE.RATE_CODE FROM CFTM_FLOATING_RATE_CODE WHERE CFTM_FLOATING_RATE_CODE.AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND CFTM_FLOATING_RATE_CODE.RECORD_STAT = 'O' ORDER BY RATE_CODE

SELECT DISTINCT COMPONENT, COMPONENT_DESCRIPTION FROM LFTMS_PRODUCT_ICCF_TEMP WHERE PRODUCT = ? AND COMPONENT NOT IN (SELECT CLASS_CODE FROM LFTM_INTEREST_CLASS A WHERE A.ALLOW_REPORTING_ONLY='Y') UNION SELECT 'PRINCIPAL', 'PRINCIPAL' FROM DUAL
SELECT CCY_CODE, CCY_NAME FROM CYTMS_CCY_DEFN WHERE RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A'
SELECT CCY_CODE, CCY_NAME FROM CYTMS_CCY_DEFN WHERE RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A'
SELECT GAAP_INDICATOR, DESCRIPTION FROM OLVW_STATIC_MAINTENANCE
SELECT CCY_RATE_TYPE , CCY_RATE_TYPE_DESC FROM CYTMS_RATE_TYPE WHERE RECORD_STAT='O' AND AUTH_STAT ='A'
SELECT CCY_CODE, CCY_NAME FROM CYTMS_CCY_DEFN WHERE RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A'
SELECT PRODUCT_CODE,PRODUCT_DESCRIPTION FROM OLTM_PRODUCT WHERE MODULE='OL'
SELECT TRN_TYPE, TRN_TYPE_DESC FROM OLTMS_REVERSAL_TRN_TYPE WHERE MODULE_CODE = 'OL' AND RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND ONCE_AUTH = 'Y'

SELECT A.MSG_TYPE, B.DESCRIPTION FROM OLTM_PRODUCT_EVENT_ADVICE A, OLTMS_MSG_TYPE B WHERE A.PRODUCT_CODE = ? AND A.MSG_TYPE = B.MSG_TYPE AND A.MSG_TYPE NOT IN (SELECT MESSAGE_CODE FROM OLTMS_PRODUCT_STATUS_ADVICES WHERE PRODUCT = ? AND STATUS = ?) UNION SELECT MSG_TYPE, DESCRIPTION FROM OLTMS_MSG_TYPE C WHERE MODULE = 'OL' AND MSG_TYPE NOT IN (SELECT MESSAGE_CODE FROM OLTMS_PRODUCT_STATUS_ADVICES WHERE PRODUCT = ? AND STATUS = ?)

SELECT ROLE_CODE, ROLE_DESCRIPTION FROM OLTBS_ACCROLE A, OLTMS_PRODUCT_ACCROLE B WHERE A.ROLE_CODE = B.ACCOUNTING_ROLE AND B.PRODUCT_CODE = ? AND B.STATUS = 'NORM' AND A.ALLOW_TRANSFER_GL = 'Y' AND A.MODULE = ? AND ROLE_CODE NOT IN (SELECT ACCOUNT_ROLE FROM OLTMS_PRODUCT_STATUS_GL WHERE PRODUCT = ? AND STATUS = ?)
SELECT STATUS_CODE, DESCRIPTION FROM OLTMS_CONTRACT_STATUSES WHERE RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND STATUS_TYPE = 'C'
SELECT DISCLOSURE_CODE, DISCLOSURE_DESCRIPTION FROM LBTMS_DISCLOSURE WHERE AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND RECORD_STAT = 'O'
SELECT FIN_CENTRE,FIN_CENTRE_DESC FROM OLTM_FIN_CENTRE WHERE RECORD_STAT='O' AND AUTH_STAT='A'
SELECT DAY,VALUE FROM OLVW_STATEMENT_DAY WHERE INDICATOR = DECODE(?, 'A','A', 'Q','A', 'S','A','M','D', 'F','F', 'W','F', 'D','D')ORDER BY VALUE
